Running in docker container locally:
docker run -p 9099:9090 -d -v /tmp/prometheus.yml:/etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml --name prometheus prom/prometheus

Config file can be found in the container under /etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml

Example basic config (prometheus.yml):
global:
  scrape_interval:     15s
  evaluation_interval: 15s

scrape_configs:
  - job_name: 'my-app'
    static_configs:
    - targets: ['localhost:8080']
